events.name: 移動（ラストダンジョン３）
移動（ラストダンジョン５）

parameters: \C[17][Lucia]\C[0] I told you, you have no chance of winning.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Whether it's you or Regnus Grahardt... I've been severely underestimated,
haven't I?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] You should know my true strength better than anyone. Ever since you sealed my
magic, I've fought various enemies and have completely regained my former power.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] No, I've even awakened a power greater than before. You were the one who chose
me as the leading magician of the imperial capital Jupiterino. If you keep
looking down on me, you'll get burned in ways you'd never expect. A direct-line
magician is not invincible.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] You've awakened as a direct-line magician and strayed from the path. I will
avenge Lady Reishia right here and now by defeating you, her daughter.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] You always remember the past, don't you? That's so like you.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Ever since I awakened as a direct-line magician, the magicians of Valentina,
who never paid me any mind before, have taken notice of me. Everything is
different from that time.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Compared to Valentina's high-ranking magicians, your magical talent is as
insignificant as a cat's forehead. It's laughable.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] There's nothing more to discuss with you.
